to all the best schools

392
00:28:52,167 --> 00:28:54,203
and had grown up
in polite society.

393
00:28:55,007 --> 00:28:58,966
He had a prodigious talent
as an artist

394
00:29:00,087 --> 00:29:02,237
and was much sought after

395
00:29:02,407 --> 00:29:04,398
when it came to
the documenting

396
00:29:04,567 --> 00:29:08,799
