in society in a portrait.

397
00:29:08,967 --> 00:29:11,800
Well, it was in this
latter capacity

398
00:29:11,967 --> 00:29:15,801
that he was commissioned
by a wealthy landowner

399
00:29:15,967 --> 00:29:19,403
to capture his daughter's
virginal beauty.

400
00:29:19,527 --> 00:29:22,564
Well, of course,
they fell deeply in love

401
00:29:22,687 --> 00:29:25,360
and she became pregnant.

402
00:29:28,767 --> 00:29:32,555
Poor Candyman.

403
00:29:34,327 --> 00:29:37,160
