a terrible revenge.

404
00:29:38,567 --> 00:29:43,243
He paid a pack of
brutal hooligans to do the deed.

405
00:29:43,367 --> 00:29:48,043
They chased Candyman
through the town to Cabrini Green

406
00:29:48,207 --> 00:29:52,041
