to saw off his right hand

407
00:29:52,207 --> 00:29:53,959
with a rusty blade.

408
00:29:54,127 --> 00:29:57,244
No one came to his aid.

409
00:29:58,847 --> 00:30:01,077
But this was just the beginning
of his ordeal.

410
00:30:01,247 --> 00:30:04,557
Nearby there was
an apiary.

411
00:30:04,647 --> 00:30:07,639
Dozens of hives,
filled with hungry bees.

412
00:30:09,967 --> 00:30:13,880
They smashed the hives
and stole the honeycomb

413
00:30:14,047 --> 00:30:17,005
and smeared it over
his prone, naked body.

414
00:30:19,207 --> 00:30:22,358
Candyman was stung
to death by the bees.

415
00:30:24,207 --> 00:30:27,199
They burned his body
on a giant pyre

416
00:30:27,327 --> 00:30:29,795
then scattered his ashes
over Cabrini Green.

