I'm sure we can arrange a visit.

818
01:04:04,647 --> 01:04:06,160
A visit?

819
01:04:06,327 --> 01:04:07,919
Have I been committed?

820
01:04:13,687 --> 01:04:17,077
Do you really think
these restraints are necessary?

821
01:04:20,167 --> 01:04:22,442
Helen, this...

822
01:04:22,607 --> 01:04:24,165
is a writ of detention

823
01:04:24,327 --> 01:04:26,557
from the state
attorney's office.

824
01:04:26,727 --> 01:04:28,445
Now, for
the past month...

825
01:04:28,607 --> 01:04:30,916
- Month?
- Yes.

826
01:04:31,047 --> 01:04:35,086
...we have been stabilizing you
on a heavy dosage of Thorazine.

827
01:04:35,247 --> 01:04:38,205
You probably remember
very little or nothing.

828
01:04:38,367 --> 01:04:40,198
Get me my attorney.

829
01:04:40,367 --> 01:04:42,437
I'm working for
your defence.

830
01:04:42,647 --> 01:04:45,923
We have to assess
your ability to stand trial.

831
01:04:46,087 --> 01:04:50,444
Helen, you've been charged
with first-degree murder.

832
01:04:59,407 --> 01:05:02,365
Why don't you tell me
what happened in your apartment?

833
01:05:27,847 --> 01:05:29,041
'Oh!'

834
01:05:32,007 --> 01:05:33,565
The night
you were admitted

835
01:05:33,727 --> 01:05:36,195
did the killer
appear to you?

836
01:05:36,327 --> 01:05:38,158
'Murderer!

837
01:05:38,327 --> 01:05:39,396
'Murderer!

838
01:05:39,527 --> 01:05:41,324
'Murderer!

839
01:05:41,487 --> 01:05:42,886
'Help me!

840
01:05:44,527 --> 01:05:46,677
'He's here!

841
01:05:46,847 --> 01:05:48,326
'He's under the bed!

842
01:05:48,487 --> 01:05:49,761
'No!

843
01:05:49,927 --> 01:05:51,121
'Help me!'

844
01:05:51,287 --> 01:05:52,606
I don't understand.

845
01:05:52,727 --> 01:05:54,877
'Help! Please!

846
01:05:55,087 --> 01:05:56,076
'He's here!

847
01:05:56,287 --> 01:05:58,198
'Help me! Help me!

848
01:05:58,327 --> 01:05:59,442
'Please!

849
01:06:00,527 --> 01:06:01,676
'He's under the bed!

850
01:06:01,807 --> 01:06:02,876
'He's under the bed!'

851
01:06:03,087 --> 01:06:04,281
That's not possible.

852
01:06:04,407 --> 01:06:06,079
'Bring me 1,000 mils!'

853
01:06:11,287 --> 01:06:12,606
Bernadette...

854
01:06:22,487 --> 01:06:24,398
I'm not capable of that.

855
01:06:30,327 --> 01:06:33,399
No matter what's going wrong...

856
01:06:33,847 --> 01:06:35,280
I know one thing...

857
01:06:35,447 --> 01:06:37,165
...that no part of me,

858
01:06:37,327 --> 01:06:39,397
no matter how hidden

859
01:06:39,527 --> 01:06:41,006
is capable of that.

860
01:06:47,847 --> 01:06:49,200
I can prove it.

861
01:06:49,327 --> 01:06:50,555
How?

862
01:06:53,527 --> 01:06:55,006
I can call him.

863
01:07:05,887 --> 01:07:08,880
Candyman...

864
01:07:09,047 --> 01:07:10,844
Candyman...

865
01:07:10,967 --> 01:07:12,400
Candyman...

866
01:07:22,127 --> 01:07:24,322
...Candyman.

867
01:07:44,367 --> 01:07:45,959
Oh! Oh!

868
01:07:57,727 --> 01:08:00,036
You're mine now.

869
01:08:00,167 --> 01:08:05,605
Tonight our congregation
shall witness a new... miracle.

870
01:08:24,367 --> 01:08:25,516
Dr Burke?

871
01:08:30,087 --> 01:08:31,759
Dr Burke?

872
01:08:31,927 --> 01:08:33,519
Dr Burke!

873
01:08:33,687 --> 01:08:35,917
Please answer us!

874
01:08:36,087 --> 01:08:38,123
Dr Burke!

875
01:09:07,127 --> 01:09:10,403
Code nine to ward b-5, stat.

876
01:09:16,367 --> 01:09:18,005
Check the west wing.

877
01:09:21,127 --> 01:09:22,401
Let's go!

878
01:09:22,567 --> 01:09:23,795
Go, go, go!

879
01:09:25,727 --> 01:09:28,799
Do we have a direction on this one?
Where is she?

880
01:09:49,447 --> 01:09:51,244
Please be home, Trevor.

881
01:09:51,367 --> 01:09:52,641
Please be home.

882
01:10:47,967 --> 01:10:49,400
Get out of my home.

883
01:10:52,007 --> 01:10:53,804
Trevor!

884
01:10:53,967 --> 01:10:55,639
What's the matter, sweetie pie?

885
01:10:55,807 --> 01:10:57,798
Did you make another little boo-boo?

886
01:10:58,967 --> 01:11:01,083
What are you doing here?

887
01:11:01,247 --> 01:11:03,886
I live here, remember?

888
01:11:04,047 --> 01:11:05,605
Call the hospital.

889
01:11:09,607 --> 01:11:11,643
Don't touch the phone.

890
01:11:25,167 --> 01:11:26,759
What's the matter, Trevor?

891
01:11:29,047 --> 01:11:31,163
Scared of something?

892
01:11:42,647 --> 01:11:45,241
I hate the color scheme.

893
01:11:48,167 --> 01:11:49,600
What were you going to do?

894
01:11:49,767 --> 01:11:51,962
Wait till I got out
before you told me?!

895
01:11:52,767 --> 01:11:53,961
Helen...

896
01:11:54,127 --> 01:11:56,482
But you knew
I was never coming out,

897
01:11:56,647 --> 01:11:57,841
didn't you?

898
01:11:59,047 --> 01:12:01,436
I think we should call the hospital.

899
01:12:04,807 --> 01:12:06,206
OK.

900
01:12:09,367 --> 01:12:10,277
Go on.

901
01:12:12,327 --> 01:12:13,601
Go on.

902
01:12:13,807 --> 01:12:15,559
Is that what you want to do?

903
01:12:17,167 --> 01:12:19,886
Call them.

904
01:12:44,087 --> 01:12:47,124
I'm not a murderer.

905
01:12:47,647 --> 01:12:49,877
I'm not.

906
01:12:50,447 --> 01:12:53,996
Trevor, you were all I had left.

907
01:12:56,047 --> 01:12:57,241
Oh...

908
01:13:15,047 --> 01:13:16,366
It's over.

909
01:13:28,047 --> 01:13:31,357
If you'd like to make a call,
please hang up and try again.

910
01:13:50,487 --> 01:13:54,082
They will all abandon you.

911
01:14:04,247 --> 01:14:09,480
All you have left
is my desire for you.

912
01:17:49,407 --> 01:17:50,840
Helen.

913
01:17:53,327 --> 01:17:55,397
You came to me.

914
01:17:57,567 --> 01:17:59,000
The child.

915
01:18:01,207 --> 01:18:02,959
We had a deal.

916
01:18:03,167 --> 01:18:05,476
Surrender to me now

917
01:18:05,647 --> 01:18:08,764
and he shall be unharmed.

918
01:18:20,167 --> 01:18:21,885
We have a bargain.

919
01:18:22,047 --> 01:18:23,844
But I'm afraid.

920
01:18:23,967 --> 01:18:26,686
Do you fear the pain
or what is beyond?

921
01:18:26,847 --> 01:18:28,280
Both.

922
01:18:28,447 --> 01:18:32,156
The pain, I can assure you,
will be exquisite.

923
01:18:32,327 --> 01:18:35,876
As for our deaths,
there is nothing to fear.

924
01:18:36,047 --> 01:18:40,040
Our names will be written
on a thousand walls.

925
01:18:40,207 --> 01:18:41,959
Our crimes told

926
01:18:42,127 --> 01:18:45,676
and retold
by our faithful believers.

927
01:18:45,847 --> 01:18:49,760
We shall die together
in front of their very eyes

928
01:18:49,927 --> 01:18:52,202
and give them something

929
01:18:52,367 --> 01:18:54,164
to be haunted by.

930
01:18:54,287 --> 01:18:55,766
Come with me

931
01:18:56,847 --> 01:18:59,281
and be immortal.

932
01:19:12,247 --> 01:19:13,396
No!

933
01:19:21,807 --> 01:19:23,798
No!

934
01:19:40,767 --> 01:19:42,564
Hush.

935
01:19:44,447 --> 01:19:45,880
Hush.

936
01:19:46,047 --> 01:19:48,880
You're mine now.

937
01:19:49,007 --> 01:19:52,124
It's time for a new miracle.

938
01:21:10,447 --> 01:21:13,519
It was always you, Helen.

939
01:21:13,687 --> 01:21:15,803
It was always you.

940
01:22:29,447 --> 01:22:31,677
He's here.

941
01:23:04,207 --> 01:23:05,526
I'm coming.

942
01:23:11,487 --> 01:23:12,966
It's OK.

943
01:23:13,127 --> 01:23:15,721
Check it out, man.

944
01:23:17,647 --> 01:23:19,638
Oh, yes.

945
01:23:19,807 --> 01:23:22,275
What happened?

946
01:23:22,447 --> 01:23:25,757
We got the Candyman out there.

947
01:23:25,927 --> 01:23:28,122
I saw him go in there.

948
01:23:28,367 --> 01:23:30,119
Candyman's in there.

949
01:23:30,287 --> 01:23:31,800
I saw him.

950
01:23:36,927 --> 01:23:38,724
I knew you'd come.

951
01:23:40,127 --> 01:23:41,924
Burn him.

952
01:23:46,087 --> 01:23:47,998
Hush.

953
01:23:48,167 --> 01:23:51,796
Burn him, burn him,
burn him, burn him...

954
01:23:54,247 --> 01:23:57,159
Burn him, burn him!

955
01:23:57,327 --> 01:23:59,795
Help!

956
01:23:59,967 --> 01:24:02,720
Burn him, burn him, burn him!

957
01:24:02,887 --> 01:24:05,117
Help... help me!

958
01:24:05,287 --> 01:24:07,118
Burn him, burn him!

959
01:24:07,287 --> 01:24:10,359
You lied to me!

960
01:24:10,487 --> 01:24:14,480
We must be on our way now,
you and I.

961
01:24:14,647 --> 01:24:16,956
Our bones will soon be ashes

962
01:24:17,127 --> 01:24:19,846
and we shall never

963
01:24:20,007 --> 01:24:21,360
be separated again.

964
01:24:21,527 --> 01:24:22,755
Let me go.

965
01:24:22,887 --> 01:24:24,161
I cannot.

966
01:24:24,327 --> 01:24:27,160
We are already dead.

967
01:24:34,647 --> 01:24:36,160
Helen!

968
01:25:09,847 --> 01:25:11,644
Come back to me!

969
01:25:22,727 --> 01:25:24,558
Come back!

970
01:26:31,247 --> 01:26:34,364
We commend to almighty God
our sister Helen

971
01:26:34,527 --> 01:26:37,200
and we commit her body
to the ground.

972
01:26:37,367 --> 01:26:40,803
Earth to earth,
ashes to ashes, dust to dust.

973
01:26:40,967 --> 01:26:44,277
The lord bless her and keep her
and give her peace.

974
01:26:44,407 --> 01:26:46,363
God of holiness and power

975
01:26:46,487 --> 01:26:49,718
accept our prayers on behalf
of your servant Helen.

976
01:26:49,847 --> 01:26:52,077
Do not count
her deeds against her.

977
01:26:52,327 --> 01:26:55,444
For in her heart she desired
to do your will.

978
01:26:55,567 --> 01:26:57,364
May almighty God bless you

979
01:26:57,567 --> 01:27:00,161
the Father and the Son
and the Holy Spirit.

980
01:27:08,087 --> 01:27:10,806
My God, look at that.

981
01:27:12,967 --> 01:27:14,798
Trevor?

982
01:28:26,127 --> 01:28:27,685
Trevor?

983
01:28:28,807 --> 01:28:31,367
What is it?

984
01:28:31,527 --> 01:28:33,245
Trevor, are you all right?

985
01:28:33,407 --> 01:28:35,921
Yeah, I'm fine.

986
01:28:36,047 --> 01:28:38,686
Aren't you hungry?

987
01:28:38,847 --> 01:28:40,280
No, I'm OK.

988
01:28:40,447 --> 01:28:42,517
I'll eat a little bit later.

989
01:28:42,687 --> 01:28:46,043
I was going to make us
a nice dinner.

990
01:28:46,247 --> 01:28:47,885
OK, whatever.

991
01:29:28,247 --> 01:29:31,478
Hey, why don't you help me
make the salad?

992
01:29:32,887 --> 01:29:35,685
OK, I'll be there
in a minute.

993
01:29:44,887 --> 01:29:46,639
Helen...

994
01:29:55,487 --> 01:29:58,081
Oh, Helen.

995
01:30:02,727 --> 01:30:04,365
Helen.

996
01:30:09,927 --> 01:30:11,645
Helen.

997
01:30:17,487 --> 01:30:19,284
Helen.

998
01:30:19,607 --> 01:30:21,598
Ow.

999
01:30:25,967 --> 01:30:27,923
What's the matter, Trevor?

1000
01:30:28,047 --> 01:30:30,038
Scared of something?

1001
01:30:39,807 --> 01:30:41,957
Trevor?

1002
01:30:42,127 --> 01:30:44,800
My God, Trevor?

1003
01:30:44,967 --> 01:30:46,036
Trevor?

1004
01:30:47,247 --> 01:30:49,078
Trevor!
